paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses a case of transthyretin cardiac amyloidosis (ATTR) in an elderly woman, but no specific genetic variants in the TTR gene are reported.

challenges: No specific TTR variants were reported in the paper.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the clinical presentation and diagnosis of ATTR, specifically wild-type ATTR, without identifying any genetic variants in the TTR gene.
